snippet.textDisplay:
Loved it to the core
Pranaam and Pailag to Kamla Devi ji ,Digvijay bhai and Neha kakkar mam.
Hey, Coke Studio please do one such collab with our very own
GARHRATAN OF UTTARAKHAND - SHRI NARENDRA SINGH NEGI JI
His songs touches every Uttarakhandi's (Pahadi's) heart.
Be it Uttarakhand Festivals (song name - Hey Ji Saaryunmaa), Relations(Dofra ka batoi, Dadu meri ulyaru jikudi) , Flowers, valleys , Devi Devtas, Mountains , Water(Thando re Thando), Corruption, Hard lifestyle of Pahadi people etc
"HIMALA HAAUN KAUTA" song (which connects Garhwal and Jaunsar)
"PARVATI KO METUDA DESH" recent collab of Late. Prahlad Mehra ji and Negi ji.
He has written, composed, and sung songs on every subject which makes up Uttarakhand's Culture.
At last A big Heartfelt Thankyou for SONCHADI
Thankyou Kamla Devi Ji for your Authentic Pahadi voice
Jai Badri Vishal🚩
Jai Devbhoomi Uttarakhand♥
